hadiths[34]{hadithnumber,text}:
2719,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abu-Hurera ! tum log meeras ka ilm seekho aur sikhaao kyonkey ye aadha ilm hai aur ye bhulwa diya jata hai. meri ummat sey sab sey pehley yehi ilm uthaya jaeyga."
2720,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Saad bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ki bewa Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki do betiyon ko ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! ye Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki betiyan hain. wo jange-ahad mein aap key sath jihad kartey huye shaheed ho gaey they. unkey chacha ney unkey baap ka chhoda huwa sara tarka ley liya hai aur maal key baghair aurat ka nikah bhi nahin hota. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey yahan tak key meeras ki aayat nazil hui . tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Saad bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) key bhai ko bulaya aur farmaya : Saad ki dono betiyon ko uskey maal mein sey do tihai dey do . aur uski biwi ko aathwan hissa do . aur jo baqi bachey wo tum ley lo."
2721,"Hazrat Huzail bin Shurehbil (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : eik aadmi ney Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Salman bin Rabeea Bahli (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar un sey beti , poti aur sagi behan (ki virasat) ka masla daryaft kya. un dono ney farmaya : beti key liye nisf hai aur jo baqi bachey wo behan ka hai. aur (saail sey) kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas jao , wo bhi hamari taeed kerengey. us aadmi ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar masla puchha aur un dono hazraat ki baat bhi batai to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : (agar main bhi yehi fatwa dun) tab to main gumrah ho jaunga aur hidayat yafta nahin hunga , lekin main wo faisla karunga jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kya tha. beti key liye nisf hai aur poti key liye chata hissey jis sey (dono ka) kul hissa do tihai ho jaey aur jo baqi bachey wo behan ka hai."
2722,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein virasat ka eik masla pesh kya gaya jis mein dada bhi tha. to mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke aap ney isey teesra hissa ya chata hissa diya ."
2723,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamarey khandan main eik dadey ko (uskey potey key tarkey mein sey) chata hissey deney ka faisla diya ."
2724,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Zuweb bin Halhala (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik naani virasat (mein sey hissey dilwaye janey) ka mutalba ley kar Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey farmaya : Allah ki kitab (Quran majeed) main to tera koi hissey mazkur nahin aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat mein bhi tera koi hissa merey ilm mein nahin, isliye (filhaal) wapis chali ja yahan tak key main logon (Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum (sey daryaft kar lun.) uskey baad) Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney logon sey daryaft kya to Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney meri mojudgi mein naani ko chata hissa diya tha. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya tumharey sath koi aur bhi (gawah) hai? Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar wohi baat kahi jo Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney kahi thi, chunanche Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney faisla us khatoon key haq mein sadir farma diya . uskey baad eik daadi, baap sey talluq rakhney wali, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas apni meeras ( key hissey) ka mutalba ley kar aai to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki kitab mein tera koi hissa mazkur nahin. aur jo faisla Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key zamana Mubarak mein kya gaya tha wo terey liye nahin tha. aur main muqarrara hisson mein koi izafa nahin kar sakta, albatta wohi chhata hissa hai. agar tum (daadi aur naani) dono is mein shareek ho jao to wo tumharey darmiyan (nisf nisf) hoga, warna tum dono mein sey jo hogi, wo (hissa) uska ho gaya ."
2725,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jadda (naani ya daadi) ko virasat mein chata hissa diya.
2726,"Hazrat Maadaan bin abu-Talha Yaamari (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey key din khutba deney khadey huye, ya Raavi ney kaha : unhoney jumey key din khutba diya . aap ney Allah ki hamd o sanaa bayan farmaai , phir farmaya : qism hai Allah ki! main apney baad kalala key masley sey ziyada pareshan kun masla chhod kar nahin jaunga. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey) ye masla puchha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi mamley mein mujhey aisa sakht jawab nahin diya jaisa us masley mein nagawari ka izhar farmaya yahan tak key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey pehlu ya seeney mein ungli maar kar farmaya : aey umr ! tujhey mausame-garma mein nazil honey wali aayat kafi hai jo Sura Nisa key aakhir mein nazil hui hai."
2727,"Hazrat Murra bin Sharaahil (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : teen masaayel aisey hain ke agar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unki (mazeed) wazahat farma di hoti to (ye wazahat) mujhey duniya aur jo kuch sumein hai sey ziyada mehbub hoti. kalala, sood aur khilaafat."
2728,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main bimar ho gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat abu-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath pedal chal kar meri iyaadat key liye tashrif laye. mujh par ghashi taari thi, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wuzu kya aur wuzu ka kuch pani mujh par dala. (us sey mein hosh mein aa gaya.) mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! main kya karun? apney maal key barey mein kya faisla karun? tab meeras ki wo aayat nazil hui jo Sura Nisa key aakhir mein hai (وَاِنْ كَانَ رَجُلٌ يُّوْرَثُ كَللَةً ) aur jiski meeras li jati hai agar wo mard (ya aurat) kalala ho. . . aur) wo aayat utri (قُلِ اللّٰهُ يُفْتِيْكُمْ فِي الْكَلٰلَةِ ) aap sey fatwa poochhtey hain. keh dijiye : Allah Taala tumhen kalala key barey mein fatwa deta hai."
2729,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman kafir ka waris nahin hota aur kafir musalman ka waris nahin hota."
2730,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! kya aap Makka mein apney ghar mein tashrif rakhengey? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya Aqeel ney hamarey liye koi makaan ya ghar chhoda hai? Abu-Talib ki virasat Aqeel aur Talib ko mili thi aur Hazrat Jaafar aur Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) ko virasat mein sey kuch nahin mila tha kyonkey ye dono musalman they aur Aqeel aur Talib kafir they. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) usi wajeh sey kaha kartey they : momin kafir ka waris nahin hota. aur Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka irshad hai : musalman kafir ka waris nahin hota aur kafir musalman ka waris nahin hota."
2731,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do mukhtalif millaton key log eik doosrey key waris nahin hotey."
2732,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Rubab bin Huzefa bin Saeed bin saham ney Hazrat Umme Wayl bint Maamar Jumahiya sey shaadi ki. unsey unkey yahan teen betey paida huye, phir unki walida (Umme Wayl) ki wafat ho gaee to Umme Wayl key beton ko virasat mein kuch zamin aur ghulamon ki wala mili. Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) un (beton) ko ley kar Sham gaey, (wahan) Amwas key taaoon mein wo (sab betey) faut ho gaey, chunanche Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu) unkey usba honey ki wajeh sey unkey waris huye. jab Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) Sham sey wapis aaye to Maamar key beton ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki adaalat main apni behan (Umme Wayl) ki wala key husool key liye daawa kar diya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main tumharey darmiyan usi irshad key mutabiq faisla karunga jo mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna hai : beta ya baap jo wala hasil kerey. wo uskey usba ko milegi, chahey koi ho. (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney) farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye faisla hamarey haq mein dey diya . aur us mazmoon ki eik tehreer likh kar hamen di jis par Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit aur eik aadmi (Raziallahu anhum) ki gawahi sabt thi . uskey baad khalifa abdul-Malik bin Marwan key zamana khilaafat mein us khatoon ka eik azad karda ghulam faut ho gaya, usney do hazar Dinar tarka chhoda . mujhey khabar mili ke us faisley mein (jo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kya tha) tabdili kar di gaee hai (faisla mazkura baala qanoon key mutabiq nahin kya gaya.) ye maamla Hisham bin Ismail key samney pesh kya gaya to usney hamen (khalifa) abdul-Malik key paas bhej diya (taake wohi us muqaddmey ka faisla keren.) chunanche hamney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki tehreer unhen dikhai. abdul-Malik ney kaha : main ye samajhta tha ke ye aisa faisla hai jis mein shak nahin kya ja sakta. main nahin samajhta tha ke Madiney walon ka ye haal ho gaya hai ke wo is mein shak karen . phir abdul-Malik ney uska faisla hamarey haq mein kar diya aur hum ab tak us ( meeras) par qaabiz hain."
2733,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka azad karda eik ghulam khajoor key darkht sey gir kar faut ho gaya . usney kuch maal chhoda tha lekin uski koi aulad ya rishtedar nahin tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski meeras uski basti key kisi aadmi ko dey do .
2734,"Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti (Hazrat amaama ya ummat Allah (Raziallahu anhuma)) jo Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) ki maa shareek behan hain, un sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mera azad karda ghulam eik beti chhod kar faut ho gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska maal merey aur uski beti key darmiyan taqseem kar diya, yani aadha mujhey diya aur aadha us ko ."
2735,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatil waris nahin hota ."
2736,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka key din (khutbey key liye) khadey huye aur (khutbey mein) farmaya : aurat apney khawind ki diyat aur uskey maal mein sey virasat (ka hissa) hasil karti hai aur khawind uski diyat aur maal mein sey virasat hasil karta hai b-sharte-ke un mein sey eik ney doosrey ko jaan-bujh kar qatl na kya ho. agar un mein sey eik ney doosrey ko jan-boojhkar qatl kya to wo na uski diyat sey virasat paeyga, na uskey maal sey. aur agar eik ney doosrey ko ghalati sey qatl kya ho (qatle-khata kya ho) to uskey maal mein sey virasat paeyga aur uski diyat mein sey virasat nahin paeyga."
2737,"Hazrat abu-Umama Asad bin Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney doosrey aadmi ko teer maar kar qatl kar diya. maqtool ka eik mamu key siwa koi waris na tha. Hazrat abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khat likh kar ye masla daryaft farmaya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney (jawab mein) khat likha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jis ka koi maula na ho, Allah aur uska Rasool uska Mola hai. aur jis ka koi waris na ho, mamu uska waris hai."
2738,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key eik Shaami Sahab Hazrat Miqdam Abu-Kareema (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs maal chhod (kar faut ho) jaey to wo maal uskey waris ka hai. aur jo koi bojh (qarz ya na baligh bachey) chhod jaey to uski zimmedaari hum par hai. ya farmaya : uski zimmedaari Allah aur uskey Rasool par hai. aur jiska koi waris nahin, uska main waris hun. uskey zimmey diyat bhi mein hi dunga aur uski virasat bhi main lunga. aur jiska koi waris na ho, mamu uska waris hai. uskey zimmey diyat bhi wohi dega aur uski virasat bhi wohi lega."
2739,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla diya tha ke eik maa key betey, yani sagey bhai eik doosrey key waris hongey, soteley bhai nahin. aadmi apney us bhai ka waris hai jo uskey baap aur uski maa ka beta hai, uska waris nahin jo uskey baap ka beta hai (maa ka nahin.)"
2740,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : as-haabul-furuz mein Allah ki kitab key mutabiq maal taqseem karo. muqarrara hissa deney key baad jo bach jaey wo qarib tareen mard key liye hai."
2741,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik shakhs faut huwa aur usney koi waris na chhoda, sirf eik ghulam tha jisey usney azad kar diya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska tarka us (azad karda ghulam) ko dey diya ."
2742,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat teen tarkey hasil karti hai. apney azad karda ghulam ka, us laawaaris bachey ka jisey usney paala ho, aur apney us bachey ka jis par usney liaan kya ho. Muhammad bin Yazeed ney kaha : is riwayat ko Hisham key ilawa kisi ney riwayat nahin kya."
2743,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab liaan ki aayat nazil hui to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat kisi qom mein us ( bachey) ko shamil karey jo (dar haqeeqat) un mein sey nahin, us aurat ka Allah sey koi talluq nahin. wo usey apni jannat mein hergiz dakhil nahin kerega. aur jo mard apney betey ko pehchan kar usey (apna beta) taslim karney sey inkar kar dey, Allah Taala qiyamat key din us sey pardey mein rahega (usey apney deedar sey mehroom rakhega) aur usey sab logon key samney ruswa kerega ."
2744,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan ka ye kaam bhi kufr hai ke wo us nasab ka dawa karey ya inkar karey jis key barey mein usey yaqeeni ilm nahin, agar-che (ye inkar ya daawa) sarahat sey na ho."
2745,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Hazrat Shuaib bin Muhammad) sey aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kisi londi sey ya kisi azad aurat sey zina kya to uska (zina key natijey mein paida honey wala) beta, na jayez aulad hai. wo (us zaani ka) waris nahin hoga, aur na uski virasat ( zaani ko) ko milegi ."
2746,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey aur wo apney dada sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis bachey ka nasab uskey baap key marney key baad, yani jis ka wo bacha kehlaata tha, us sey milaaney ka daawa kya jaey, yani us shakhs key marney key baad uskey waris us bachey ka daawa karen (ke wo faut honey waley ka beta hai, isliye hum uskey sarparast hongey, aur wo hum mein shumar hoga) uska faisla ye hai ke jo bacha us londi sey ho jis sey milaap key moqey par wo us shakhs (bachey ki baap) ki milkiyat thi to wo us sey milaaya jaeyga jisney (apney khandan mein) milaaney ka dawa kya hai. aur usey us tarkey mein sey kuch nahin milega jo us (ko milaaney) sey pehley taqseem ho chuka. aur jo meeras abhi taqseem nahin hui thi is mein sey usey hissa milega. agar uskey us baap ney usey beta taslim karney sey inkar kya tha jiska ye beta kehlaata hai to usey uskey sath nahin milaaya jaeyga. agar ye bacha us londi sey paida huwa hai jo marney waley ki milkiyat na thi, ya us azad aurat sey paida huwa hai jis sey marney waley ney zina kya tha to usey us (marney waley) sey nahin milaaya jaeyga, na usey virasat di jaeygi, agar-che wo jiska beta mashhoor hai, usney uska daawa kya ho (ke ye mujh sey hai) kyonkey ye na jayez aulad hai. ye apni maa key khandan sey shumar hoga, wo jo koi bhi hon, chahey uski maa azad ho ya londi. Muhammad bin Rashid (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : is sey murad wo taqseem hai jo Islam sey pehley jahiliyat mein ho chuki."
2747,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wala ko bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya."
2748,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wala ko bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya."
2749,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo meeras jahiliyat mein taqseem ho chuki , wo jahiliyat ki taqseem key mutabiq qaaim rahegi. aur jiski taqseem sey pehley Islam aa gaya (faut honey wala aur uskey waris musalman ho gaey) to wo Islam key usoolon key mutabiq taqseem hogi ."
2750,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab bacha aawaz nikaley to uska janaza padha jaeyga aur wo waris hoga ."
2751,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah aur Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bacha waris nahin hoga yahan tak key aawaz key sath cheekhey. Raavi ney kaha : aawaz nikalney ka matlab hai ke wo roey ya cheekhey ya chheenk maarey."
2752,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! ehle-kitab key us shakhs key barey mein kya qanoon hai jo eik aadmi key haath par Islam qubul kerey? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zindagi aur maut dono haalaton mein uska us sey talluq sab logon sey ziyada hai."
